name: Harvest Low Volatility Canadian Equity ETF
longDescription: The Harvest Low Volatility Canadian Equity Income ETF will invest its assets, directly or indirectly, in a diversified portfolio of Equity Securities of companies primarily listed on a Canadian exchange. The Harvest ETF may invest in one or more exchange traded funds or invest directly in the underlying securities. In selecting the portfolio constituents, consideration is given to various quantitative and qualitative factors such as growth, financial positioning, profitability, and risk characteristics. The Harvest Low Volatility Canadian Equity ETF will seek to provide Unitholders with (i) the opportunity for capital appreciation and (ii) lower overall volatility of portfolio returns than is otherwise experienced.
